{{unreferenced|date=November 2018}} {{Underlinked|date=October 2017}} {{Infobox newspaper | name = Kosova Sot | image = Kosova Sot Logo.png| | image_size = 200px | caption = | type = Daily [[newspaper]] | format = | foundation = 1998 | ceased publication = | price = | owner = | political position = | publisher = | editor = | staff = | circulation = | headquarters = [[Pristina]] | ISSN = | website = {{URL|http://www.kosova-sot.info/|Official website}} }}
'''''Kosova Sot''''' (English: Kosovo Today) is a newspaper published in Kosovo. Preparations for the publication of the newspaper began in 1997 and the first newspaper was published on 12 September 1998. The founder of the daily newspaper is Mr. Ruzhdi Kadriu. Editor-in-chief and director of the daily newspaper ''Kosova Sot'' until 2014 was Margarita Kadriu. ''Kosova Sot'' continues to be the leading newspaper in Kosovo and it has independent editorial policy. It is published in hard copy as well as online at www.kosova-sot.info.
