'''Qinghai Television ''' (QHTV), {{zh|s=青海卫视|p=Qīnghǎi Diànshìtái}}) is a [[television network]] under [[Hunan Broadcasting System]] (HBS) in the [[Xining]] city and [[Qinghai]] province area. It was founded on January 1, 1971. QHTV currently broadcasts in [[Standard Chinese|Chinese]], [[Southern Mongolian|Mongolian]], [[Standard Tibetan|Tibetan]] and [[Salar language|Salar]].

